title: Freelee's 4000 Calorie Per Day Diet and Its Dissidents.
description:
If your interest is purely in the diet, you can jump to 18:28 (as this is a conversation that covers many topics, starting with the study of languages).
This is the (complete) conversation alluded to in the video just uploaded (title: "Don't Mention Durianrider…").  Previously, this video was only available to Patreon subscribers, and you can support the creation of new content of this kind for $1 per month at Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/a_bas_le_ciel/posts
